<plot>Mr. Baker gives his secretary Winnie Winkle, breadwinner, the afternoon off. Her little nephew, Perry Winkle, and has club house pals, the Rinky Dinks, have a baseball game with a rival gang. After the game, Winnie takes Perry and one of his pals to his dancing lesson at the St. Vitas School. There, a frog contributes to a new choreography.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?229540</url></doc>
